{"lemma":"صَحِيفَةٌ","slug":"صَحِيفَةٌ","root":"ص.ح.ف","root_slug":"ص-ح-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ح-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23818"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"newspaper"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"journal, ephemeris"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a loose piece of paper on which has been written, a sheet, letters, paper","examples":[{"text":"أَرْسِلِي إِلَيْنَا بِالصُّحُفِ نَنْسَخُهَا فِي الْمَصَاحِفِ ثُمَّ نَرُدُّهَا إِلَيْكِ","english":"Send to us the sheets so we can transcribe manuscripts from them and thereafter we will return them."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"an amount of paper in a bound work, a page or leaf of a physical book, a sheet such as a كُرَّاسَة (kurrāsa), record"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"surface, exterior, outer skin, epidermis"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Diminutive of صَحْفَة (ṣaḥfa); a saucer.","tags":["diminutive","form-of"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sˤa.ħiː.fa/","/sˤu.ħaj.fa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23818","headword_ar":"صَحِيفَةٌ","root":"SHf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A written piece of paper"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, Mgh, Msb) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of skin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a writing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing written; a book,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"volume; a letter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an epistle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbN","text_ar":"كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) [syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbN","text_ar":"كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in all of these senses; in the last of them in an anecdote related in Freytag's Arab. Prov. i. 721-2, and in Har p. 119, q. v.;] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion of a book, such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~aAsap","text_ar":"كُرَّاسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a register;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for] in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inoqaAE","text_ar":"اـِنْقَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a title of several books, it is said that] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~aAsap","text_ar":"كُرَّاسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSoHaf","text_ar":"مُصْحَف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfap","text_ar":"صَحِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAb","text_ar":"كِتَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafotar","text_ar":"دَفْتَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"are one: (MA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHufN","text_ar":"صُحُفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHofN","text_ar":"صُحْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a contraction of the former, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHaAy^ifu","text_ar":"صَحَايِفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaAy^inu","text_ar":"سَفَايِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safiynapN","text_ar":"سَفِينَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Lth, O;) the first of these pls. anomalous, (Lth, Sb, O, K,) the sing. being likened to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDiytN","text_ar":"قَضِيتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, O, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaliybN","text_ar":"قَلِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ragiyfN","text_ar":"رَغِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) of which the pls. are"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quDubN","text_ar":"قُضُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, O, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qulubN","text_ar":"قُلُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rugufN","text_ar":"رُغُفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O:) [or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfN","text_ar":"صَحِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be its original, as well as regular, sing.:] see the next preceding paragraph."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHufi A_ibor`hiyma wamuwsaY","text_ar":"صُحُفِ اـِبْرٰهِيمَ وَمُوسَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [lxxxvii. last verse], means [In"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the books of Abraham and Moses;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the books revealed to Abraham and Moses."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfapN","text_ar":"صَحِيفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also means The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"record of the actions"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anyone, that is kept in heaven: (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~N","text_ar":"رَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfanuhu sawodaA='u","text_ar":"صَحِيفَنُهُ سَوْدَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The record of his actions is black;"},{"kind":"text","text":"a phrase often used in the present day, in speaking of a bad man.] Mohammad [the Hanafee Imám] speaks of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHuf","text_ar":"صُحُف"},{"kind":"text","text":"not written upon; saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA_ino","text_ar":"فَاـِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAnati Als~ariqapu SuHufFA layosa fiyhaA kitaAbN","text_ar":"كَانَتِ السَّرِقَةُ صُحُفًا لَيْسَ فِيهَا كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And if the stolen property be papers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"books, not having any writing upon them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh. [See, again,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~N","text_ar":"رَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfapN","text_ar":"صَحِيفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A plank, board,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaf,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a door; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHaAy^ifu","text_ar":"صَحَايِفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[from which it is perhaps formed by transposition, or it may be tropical in this sense]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfN","text_ar":"صَحِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MA.) ―         -b3-  Also (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"external skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scarf-skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the face: (O, TA:) or as some say, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that fronts one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfN","text_ar":"صَحِيفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or this may be used, in a verse in which it occurs, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfap","text_ar":"صَحِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-  One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHaAy^ifu mino $aHomK","text_ar":"صَحَايِفُ مِنْ شَحْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Layers of fat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nyr","text_ar":"نير"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["MA","Mgh","Msb","S","O","K","TA","Lth","Sb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}